---
const APP_URL = 'https://app.erdify.com';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="description" content="ERDify Developer Center — MCP 연동, REST API, SDK 레퍼런스" />
  <title>Developer Center — ERDify</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard@v1.3.9/dist/web/variable/pretendardvariable-dynamic-subset.min.css" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --blue: #0064E0;
      --blue-hover: #0143B5;
      --font: 'Pretendard Variable', Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
      --bg:    #080f1a;
      --bg2:   #0d1726;
      --bg3:   #111f33;
      --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      --text:  #ffffff;
      --sub:   rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { font-family: var(--font); background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }
    .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav class="nav">
  <div class="container nav-inner">
    <a href="/" class="logo"><img src="/logo-white.svg" alt="ERDify" style="width:138px;height:36px;display:block;" /></a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/docs/mcp-integration">MCP 연동</a>
      <a href="/docs/api-reference">REST API</a>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-right">
      <a href="/" class="nav-ghost">← 사이트로</a>
      <a href={`${APP_URL}/settings/api`} class="nav-btn">API 키 발급</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-glow"></div>
  <div class="container hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <div class="eyebrow">Developer Center</div>
      <h1>ERDify와<br />함께 빌드하세요</h1>
      <p>MCP로 AI 도구에 연결하거나, REST API로 직접 통합하세요.<br />API 키 하나로 모든 연동을 시작할 수 있습니다.</p>
      <div class="hero-btns">
        <a href="/docs/mcp-integration" class="btn-primary">MCP 연동 시작하기 →</a>
        <a href="/docs/api-reference" class="btn-outline">API 레퍼런스</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="chat-window">
      <div class="cw-bar">
        <span class="dot" style="background:#FF5F57"></span>
        <span class="dot" style="background:#FEBC2E"></span>
        <span class="dot" style="background:#28C840"></span>
        <span class="cw-title">Cursor — AI Chat</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cw-body">
        <div class="cw-msg cw-msg--user">결제 관련 테이블 추가해줘. orders랑 order_items 필요해</div>
        <div class="cw-msg cw-msg--ai">
          <span class="cw-label">AI (ERDify MCP)</span>
          현재 스키마를 확인하고 테이블을 추가하겠습니다.
        </div>
        <div class="cw-tool"><span class="cw-t-dot"></span><span class="cw-t-fn">add_entity</span><span class="cw-t-arg">"orders"</span><span class="cw-t-ok">✓</span></div>
        <div class="cw-tool"><span class="cw-t-dot"></span><span class="cw-t-fn">add_entity</span><span class="cw-t-arg">"order_items"</span><span class="cw-t-ok">✓</span></div>
        <div class="cw-tool"><span class="cw-t-dot"></span><span class="cw-t-fn">add_relationship</span><span class="cw-t-arg">orders → users</span><span class="cw-t-ok">✓</span></div>
        <div class="cw-msg cw-msg--ai">완료됐습니다. ERD에 반영되었습니다.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- QUICK START -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow">연동 방법 선택</p>
    <h2 class="sec-title">두 가지 방법으로 연결하세요</h2>
    <div class="qs-grid">
      <a href="/docs/mcp-integration" class="qs-card qs-card--hl">
        <span class="qs-icon">🤖</span>
        <h3>MCP 연동</h3>
        <p>Cursor, Claude Desktop, Gemini CLI, Codex CLI에서 자연어로 ERD를 읽고 수정합니다.</p>
        <div class="qs-tags"><span>Cursor</span><span>Claude Desktop</span><span>Gemini CLI</span><span>Codex CLI</span></div>
        <span class="qs-link">가이드 보기 →</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/docs/api-reference" class="qs-card">
        <span class="qs-icon">⚡</span>
        <h3>REST API</h3>
        <p>HTTP 요청으로 스키마를 조회·수정하고 DDL을 내보냅니다. JS·Python SDK를 지원합니다.</p>
        <div class="qs-tags"><span>cURL</span><span>JavaScript</span><span>Python</span></div>
        <span class="qs-link">레퍼런스 보기 →</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TOOLS -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow">개발자 도구</p>
    <h2 class="sec-title">필요한 모든 것이 준비돼 있습니다</h2>
    <div class="tools-grid">
      <div class="tool">
        <span class="tool-icon">📐</span>
        <h4>MCP 서버</h4>
        <p>npx 한 줄로 실행. 별도 설치 없이 바로 연결됩니다.</p>
        <code>npx @erdify/mcp-server@latest</code>
      </div>
      <div class="tool">
        <span class="tool-icon">📦</span>
        <h4>JavaScript SDK</h4>
        <p>TypeScript 지원 공식 JS SDK. Node.js·브라우저 모두 지원.</p>
        <code>npm install @erdify/sdk</code>
      </div>
      <div class="tool">
        <span class="tool-icon">🐍</span>
        <h4>Python SDK</h4>
        <p>Python 3.8+ 공식 SDK. pip으로 설치하세요.</p>
        <code>pip install erdify</code>
      </div>
      <div class="tool">
        <span class="tool-icon">🔑</span>
        <h4>API 키</h4>
        <p>모든 연동에 사용하는 단일 키. 앱 설정에서 발급합니다.</p>
        <a href={`${APP_URL}/settings/api`} class="tool-link">키 발급하기 →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="tool">
        <span class="tool-icon">⬇</span>
        <h4>DDL 내보내기</h4>
        <p>MySQL·PostgreSQL·MariaDB DDL을 API로 바로 내보냅니다.</p>
        <a href="/docs/api-reference" class="tool-link">API 보기 →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="tool">
        <span class="tool-icon">📡</span>
        <h4>Webhook</h4>
        <p>ERD 변경 이벤트를 Webhook으로 수신합니다.</p>
        <span class="coming-soon">Coming Soon</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="cta-wrap">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-box">
      <div>
        <h2>API 키 하나로 시작하세요</h2>
        <p>MCP든 REST API든, 모두 같은 키로 연결됩니다.</p>
      </div>
      <a href={`${APP_URL}/settings/api`} class="btn-primary">API 키 발급하기 →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer class="footer">
  <div class="container footer-inner">
    <span class="footer-copy">© 2026 ERDify. All rights reserved.</span>
    <div class="footer-links">
      <a href="/docs/mcp-integration">MCP 연동</a>
      <a href="/docs/api-reference">REST API</a>
      <a href="/">사이트로</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  /* Nav */
  .nav { position:sticky; top:0; z-index:100; height:60px; background:rgba(8,15,26,0.88); backdrop-filter:blur(12px); border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); }
  .nav-inner { height:100%; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:32px; }
  .logo { flex-shrink:0; }
  .nav-links { display:flex; gap:28px; flex:1; }
  .nav-links a { font-size:14px; font-weight:500; color:var(--sub); transition:color .15s; }
  .nav-links a:hover { color:#fff; }
  .nav-right { display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:center; }
  .nav-ghost { font-size:14px; font-weight:500; color:rgba(255,255,255,.4); padding:9px 14px; border-radius:8px; transition:background .15s,color .15s; }
  .nav-ghost:hover { background:rgba(255,255,255,.07); color:rgba(255,255,255,.8); }
  .nav-btn { font-size:14px; font-weight:600; color:#fff; background:var(--blue); padding:9px 18px; border-radius:8px; transition:background .15s; }
  .nav-btn:hover { background:var(--blue-hover); }

  /* Buttons */
  .btn-primary { display:inline-block; font-size:15px; font-weight:600; color:#fff; background:var(--blue); padding:12px 24px; border-radius:10px; transition:background .15s; }
  .btn-primary:hover { background:var(--blue-hover); }
  .btn-outline { display:inline-block; font-size:15px; font-weight:600; color:rgba(255,255,255,.7); border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2); padding:12px 24px; border-radius:10px; transition:border-color .15s,color .15s; }
  .btn-outline:hover { border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.5); color:#fff; }

  /* Hero */
  .hero { padding:100px 0 80px; position:relative; overflow:hidden; }
  .hero-glow { position:absolute; top:-200px; left:50%; transform:translateX(-50%); width:800px; height:600px; background:radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(0,100,224,.18) 0%, transparent 70%); pointer-events:none; }
  .hero-inner { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:64px; align-items:center; position:relative; z-index:1; }
  .eyebrow { display:inline-block; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.1em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--blue); background:rgba(0,100,224,.15); border:1px solid rgba(0,100,224,.3); padding:5px 12px; border-radius:20px; margin-bottom:20px; }
  h1 { font-size:48px; font-weight:800; line-height:1.15; margin-bottom:20px; }
  .hero-text p { font-size:16px; line-height:1.75; color:var(--sub); margin-bottom:32px; }
  .hero-btns { display:flex; gap:12px; flex-wrap:wrap; }

  /* Chat window */
  .chat-window { background:var(--bg2); border-radius:14px; border:1px solid var(--border); overflow:hidden; box-shadow:0 24px 64px rgba(0,0,0,.5); }
  .cw-bar { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; padding:12px 16px; background:var(--bg3); border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); }
  .dot { width:10px; height:10px; border-radius:50%; flex-shrink:0; }
  .cw-title { font-size:12px; color:var(--sub); margin-left:8px; font-family:monospace; }
  .cw-body { padding:20px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:10px; }
  .cw-msg { font-size:13px; line-height:1.6; padding:10px 14px; border-radius:8px; }
  .cw-msg--user { background:rgba(0,100,224,.15); color:rgba(255,255,255,.85); align-self:flex-end; max-width:90%; }
  .cw-msg--ai { background:rgba(255,255,255,.05); color:rgba(255,255,255,.75); font-size:12.5px; }
  .cw-label { display:block; font-size:10px; font-weight:700; color:var(--blue); margin-bottom:4px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.05em; }
  .cw-tool { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; padding:6px 10px; background:rgba(0,100,224,.08); border:1px solid rgba(0,100,224,.15); border-radius:6px; font-size:11.5px; font-family:monospace; }
  .cw-t-dot { width:5px; height:5px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--blue); flex-shrink:0; }
  .cw-t-fn { color:#60a5fa; font-weight:600; }
  .cw-t-arg { color:var(--sub); flex:1; }
  .cw-t-ok { color:#34d399; font-weight:700; }

  /* Sections */
  .section { padding:80px 0; border-top:1px solid var(--border); }
  .sec-title { font-size:30px; font-weight:800; margin-bottom:40px; }

  /* Quick start */
  .qs-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:16px; }
  .qs-card { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:12px; padding:32px; background:var(--bg2); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:16px; transition:border-color .18s,box-shadow .18s; }
  .qs-card:hover { border-color:rgba(0,100,224,.4); box-shadow:0 4px 32px rgba(0,100,224,.1); }
  .qs-card--hl { border-color:rgba(0,100,224,.3); background:rgba(0,100,224,.06); }
  .qs-icon { font-size:28px; }
  .qs-card h3 { font-size:20px; font-weight:700; }
  .qs-card p { font-size:14px; color:var(--sub); line-height:1.7; }
  .qs-tags { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:6px; }
  .qs-tags span { font-size:11px; font-weight:600; color:rgba(255,255,255,.5); background:rgba(255,255,255,.07); padding:3px 10px; border-radius:20px; }
  .qs-link { font-size:14px; font-weight:700; color:var(--blue); margin-top:auto; }

  /* Tools */
  .tools-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:16px; }
  .tool { padding:28px; background:var(--bg2); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:14px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:10px; transition:border-color .15s; }
  .tool:hover { border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.15); }
  .tool-icon { font-size:24px; }
  .tool h4 { font-size:16px; font-weight:700; }
  .tool p { font-size:13px; color:var(--sub); line-height:1.65; flex:1; }
  .tool code { font-family:monospace; font-size:12px; color:#60a5fa; background:rgba(96,165,250,.1); padding:6px 10px; border-radius:6px; }
  .tool-link { font-size:13px; font-weight:600; color:var(--blue); }
  .tool-link:hover { text-decoration:underline; }
  .coming-soon { display:inline-block; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; color:rgba(255,255,255,.3); background:rgba(255,255,255,.06); padding:3px 10px; border-radius:20px; }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-wrap { padding:60px 0 80px; border-top:1px solid var(--border); }
  .cta-box { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:32px; background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(0,100,224,.15),rgba(0,100,224,.05)); border:1px solid rgba(0,100,224,.25); border-radius:20px; padding:48px 56px; }
  .cta-box h2 { font-size:26px; font-weight:800; margin-bottom:8px; }
  .cta-box p { font-size:15px; color:var(--sub); }

  /* Footer */
  .footer { border-top:1px solid var(--border); padding:24px 0; }
  .footer-inner { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; }
  .footer-copy { font-size:12px; color:rgba(255,255,255,.25); }
  .footer-links { display:flex; gap:24px; }
  .footer-links a { font-size:13px; color:rgba(255,255,255,.35); transition:color .15s; }
  .footer-links a:hover { color:rgba(255,255,255,.7); }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width:900px) {
    .hero-inner { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .chat-window { display:none; }
    .qs-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .tools-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
    .cta-box { flex-direction:column; text-align:center; padding:40px 28px; }
    .nav-links,.nav-ghost { display:none; }
  }
  @media (max-width:600px) {
    h1 { font-size:34px; }
    .tools-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  }
</style>
</body>
</html>
